com.montefiore.gaulthiergain.adhoclibrary.datalink.service

Class Service

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.montefiore.gaulthiergain.adhoclibrary.datalink.service.Service
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServiceClient, ServiceServer

    public abstract class Service
extends java.lang.Object

    This class defines the constants for connection states and message handling and aims to serve as a common interface for service ServiceClient and ServiceServer classes.
